Aim: Scan a system of web app for commen vulnerabilities Scanning Using OWASP ZAP.

Background:

Vulnerability scaming helps detect:

    -Misconfiguration
    -Outdated Software
    -Weak authentication

One of the most widely used tools is OWASP znp developed by OWASP.

Types of scamming:

Passive Scan [Safe Testing)

Active Scan [Agressive Testing]

Methodology:

1)Set up environment

  Install owasp zap

  run your web app

2)Configure Proxy

   IP Address 127.0.0.1

   Port: 8080

3)Capture Traffic

   Open your web app

   Zap records all request.

4) Perform scan

   Automatically scan traffic for:

    1 Cookie issues
    2 Information leakage
              
Project idea:

1)Create a login system that dynamically adjusts security based on risk.

2)Design a Blockchain-Integrated Multifactor Authentication (MFA) System for secure online exam.

